Class GameRomhacksRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.treescrub.spedran.requests.ResourceCollectionRequest<Game>
      • com.treescrub.spedran.requests.builders.game.GameRomhacksRequest
  • public class GameRomhacksRequest
extends ResourceCollectionRequest<Game>
    A request builder to get all derived Games (romhacks) for a given Game.
